name: Paragon V1.0
description:
This model (V1.0) is also on Hugging Face.

All my models are on Hugging Face.

A demo generation on Hugging Face is available (free, but it uses a CPU, so the generation speed is slow).

For this model I suggest you use:

EasyNegative and bad-hands-5

Recommended negative prompt:

(deformed iris, deformed pupils, semi-realistic, cgi, 3d, render, sketch, cartoon, drawing, anime, mutated hands and fingers:1.4), (deformed, distorted, disfigured:1.3), poorly drawn, bad anatomy, wrong anatomy, extra limb, missing limb, floating limbs, disconnected limbs, mutation, mutated, ugly, disgusting, amputation, easynegative, bad-hands-5


Parameters for the generation I recommend:

Euler A or DPM++ SDE Karras with 25+ steps
CFG Scale 5-12
Hires. fix with Latent or UltrasharpX4 upscaler
0 Hires steps and Denoising strength 0.35-0.7
Upscale by 1.1-2.0
ENSD 31337
Clip Skip 2


Thanks to the creators of these models for their work. Without them it would not have been possible to create this model.

  • ReV Animated by s6yx

  • Lyriel by FIKOsofter

  • NeverEnding Dream (NED) by Lykon

  • Analog Madness - Realistic model by CornmeisterNL
